          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三公府，燮理阴阳宰相家！再说，这半夜三更，大雪纷飞，你就不怕冷吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好不分晓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为国家哪顾得寒夜雪降，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有机密大事情特来商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既有机密大事，何不早讲？待我与你通报。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张千击錪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何人击錪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张千禀事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "所禀何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "府外一人，言有机密大事，要见相爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可曾问过名姓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他说是什么万里山河赵大郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来圣驾到了。快摆香案，大开正门！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喳！哎呀，原来圣驾到了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖细吹打〗。张千开门，拿灯引赵普上，同出门。赵普跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣，赵普接驾来迟，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相你休忙，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "把门的不要慌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤、赵普、张千同进门，赵匡胤中坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵普见驾，愿我皇万岁！万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相，把门者何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "门下张千。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好大胆的张千！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵普跪，张千随跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恁道是，调和鼎鼐三公府，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "燮理阴阳宰相家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请几个没头发的唐三藏？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿道是，卿道是当朝宰相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "似这等，大雪纷飞"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫寡人哪里去"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老臣知罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵普起，张千随起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恁看那银台上灯花结蕊，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一霎时瑞雪儿遍体生凉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣有内宅书房，请主避寒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掌灯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张千掌灯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将身儿且把这书房来进，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桌案上摆的是什么文章？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "桌案之上是什么书？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃半部《论语》。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "《论语》乃儿童所读，卿居相位，看它作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐家治国安天下，尽在半部《论语》中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好个“尽在半部论语中”！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "评古论今把文讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "齐家治国定家邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，圣驾在此，快来见驾！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵夫人上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣妾见驾，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启万岁：现有煖酒，臣不敢献上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呈上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张千捧酒上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张千捧酒呈。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有美酒和丞相同饮欢畅，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老臣执壶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣妾把盏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又何必劳嫂嫂捧霞觞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵匡胤饮酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃糟糠之妻，怎当万岁“嫂”称之？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是糟糠之妻不下堂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贫贱之交岂可忘？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两下和好免灾殃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄嫂梁鸿配孟光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿你夫妻们福寿安康。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫妻恩爱山海样"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤与你好比太甲伊尹降"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "琼浆玉液来欢畅"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵普"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂嫂暂请回避，孤有国事议论。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妾身归香阁，捧茶待君王。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵夫人下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。万岁，这等大雪纷飞，驾临臣门，有何国事议论？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相，寡人只为四寇呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忧只忧那河东无有能将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "河东有钱王、李王镇守。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忧只忧败国贼钱王、李王，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忧只忧百姓们受锋惊铓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忧只忧当军的持矛戈降"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启万岁：臣有四将，名唤曹彬、石守信、王全宾、潘仁美。今举四人，可能前"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去镇守。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣来见朕！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张千，传曹、石、王、潘进府参驾！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。他们都在曹彬家中，待我唤来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张千向内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！相爷有令，命曹、石、王、潘进府参驾！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘仁美 （内同白） 来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（曹彬上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹彬",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听阃外将军令，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（石守信上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "石守信",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳闻朝中天子宣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王全宾上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王全宾",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赤胆忠心来保国，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（潘仁美上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘仁美",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "匡扶社稷佐明君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹彬、石守信、王全宾、潘仁美",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣驾在此，上前见驾！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹彬、石守信、王全宾、潘仁美",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣等见驾，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹彬、石守信、王全宾、潘仁美",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站立两厢，听朕晓谕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹彬、石守信、王全宾、潘仁美",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乾德王坐相府提兵调将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左和右站四将曹、石、潘、王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "石守信取吴越扫灭钱塘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "潘仁美镇两广保随孤王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个个血战把名扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得要欺帅自为王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "犒赏三军享安康。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命曹彬带人马江南抵挡"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王全宾守四川把贼扫荡"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个个齐把元戎掌"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个个雄壮似虎狼"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个个抖擞英雄将"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休得要拆毁民房路"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一路开道民安定"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹彬"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "石守信"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王全宾"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘仁美",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣等领旨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寡人回宫去也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四员虎将气昂昂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他与孤王定家邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大宋江山归一统"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵普"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹彬"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "石守信"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王全宾"
        },
        {
          "character": "潘仁美",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣等送驾！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵匡胤",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤将他一个一个来封王。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二太监同上，引赵匡胤同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵普",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位将军，此去须要齐心，不负老夫所望！"
